snippet.title: Action Arcade Wrestling  (9/11/2010)
snippet.description:
Official description: A tribute to retro wrestling games of the past. Select from THREE different control schemes! Play multiple match types, edit arenas and create wrestlers... all for just 80 points. A winner is STILL you! Powered by Torque X.

RELEASE DATE: 9/11/2010
DEVELOPER: Action937
GENRE: Sports & Recreation
Offline players 1 - 4
Offline co-op 2
